                <note type="updated" update="general" import="tengyur-data-2217-2254_PH_new_v2.4.xml" date-time="2021-11-02T13:47:33.72Z" user="admin">The commentary on the Kudṛṣṭinirghātana distinguishes three states: a causal state, the state of fruition, and the state of working for others. In the root
